cast.overview: Father Gabriele Amorth, Chief Exorcist of the Vatican, investigates a young boy's terrifying possession and ends up uncovering a centuries-old conspiracy the Vatican has desperately tried to keep hidden.
cast.title: The Pope's Exorcist

details.biography: Carrie Munro (born 13 March 2003) is a model, artist and actress, known for The Pope's Exorcist (2023) and Annie Shared Her Location (2024). She is also a social media influencer, who rose to fame after appearing in Aj Shabeel's '100 NERDS VS 1 SUPERMODEL'. She has amassed 10.9 thousand followers on Instagram.
details.name: Carrie Munro
